<plot>Hightops Productions presents its first feature length documentary where it follows along... itself. Making Bubbles shows the trials and tribulations that one group encounters while competing in Buffalo's 48 Hour Film Festival. The range of emotions goes from laugh out loud funny, until you find yourself on the edge of your seat counting down as the team rushes to get their movie in on time. Making Bubbles answers the age old question of what do you get when you mix a complete lack of sleep with a couple cases of energy drinks and a little pop music.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353468</url></doc>
